casebody.data:
No. 28,

Misc.

Bednarik v. Alvis, Warden, et al. Petitioner pro se. C. William O’Neill, Attorney General of Ohio, and Thomas R. Lloyd, Assistant Attorney General, for respondents.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Ohio denied for the reason that the judgment below is based on state procedural grounds adequate to support it.
